title UHST Signalling Protocol

Host->Signalling Server: POST /?action=host&hostId=example
#token 
Signalling Server->Host: Host configuration
Host->Signalling Server: GET /?token=hostToken
note right of Host: EventSource Server Sent Events
Client->Signalling Server: POST /?action=join&hostId=example
Signalling Server->Client: Client configuration
Client->Signalling Server: GET /?token=clientToken
note left of Client: EventSource Server Sent Events
Client->Signalling Server: POST /?token=clientToken
Signalling Server->Host: Client Offer
Host->Signalling Server: POST /?token=hostToken
Signalling Server->Client: Host answer
Client->Signalling Server: POST /?token=clientToken
Signalling Server->Host: Client ICE Candidate
Host->Signalling Server: POST /?token=hostToken
Signalling Server->Client: Host ICE Candidate
